Dem do first international environmental conference for Poland wey I go last month.

Di Conference wey dem do for Lower Silesia, na di Environment Ministry, Rockefeller Brothers Fund and di Polish Ecological Club na dem go do am. Dem go 50 pole from government, industry, Hungarians, Czechs, Russia, Japan and America.

Di conference na entitled "Economic Mechanisms for Environmental Protection", a significant departure from East Bloc usage wey only one economic mechanism, central planning to direct industrial behaviour.

Even di emissions trading, and similar market approach to address pollution, notwithstanding sey di market no dey for Poland again.

