Some of the things wey e fit make us do na :

: - privatisation.

Polish go do 40 billion foreign debt, and skyrocket inflation, Poland must do privatisation, and eliminate subsidy to stabilize di currency, and qualify for international assistance.

Market based pollution control fit enter some capital wey go otherwise buy state machine.

But e fit also accelerate "market" by reinforcing industrial accountability, breaking state monopoly, giving managers a stake in solution, and making sure sey modernisation no dey fail to affect environmental effect.

